utilMDE
Class ArraysMDE

java.lang.Object
  utilMDE.ArraysMDE

public final class ArraysMDE
extends java.lang.Object

Utilities for manipulating arrays. This complements @link{java.util.Arrays}. Also, some routines also handle Collections.
